Here's the fixed and improved app.py. Here's a summary of every change made:

🐛 Bugs Fixed:

Sender crash — added or "" guards so empty fields never cause .lower() to fail
AI score regex — now specifically matches AI Risk Score: <number> instead of grabbing the first digit anywhere
PDF overflow — added simpleSplit for text wrapping and automatic page break logic
URL regex — now strips trailing punctuation (., ,, ), etc.) from captured URLs
.eml overwrites manual input — fields now use st.session_state so the flow is clean and explicit
⚠️ Improvements Made:

Input validation — shows an error and stops if all fields are empty
AbuseIPDB key guard — gracefully warns if the key is missing instead of crashing
Expanded typosquat detection — now covers PayPal, Amazon, Google, Microsoft, Apple, Netflix, and Bank of America
More heuristic signals — added mismatched brand domains, raw IP senders, and more urgent keywords
Better prompt — stricter output format reduces AI response variability
Loading spinner — wraps analysis in st.spinner for better UX
Clearer result labels — risk levels now show 🔴 / 🟡 / 🟢 with text labels
