To get it working, do this once:

Go to portal.azure.com → Azure Active Directory → App registrations → New registration
Name it ThreatLens AI, set redirect URI to http://localhost:8501
Add API permissions: Mail.Read, Mail.ReadBasic, User.Read (all delegated)
Create a client secret under "Certificates & secrets"
Add to your .env:
AZURE_CLIENT_ID=your_client_id
AZURE_CLIENT_SECRET=your_secret_value
AZURE_TENANT_ID=common
AZURE_REDIRECT_URI=http://localhost:8501
Install the new dependency: pip install requests
Run streamlit run app.py — the setup instructions are built into the UI if credentials are missing
